      "title": "2026-06-01",
      "instruction": "Happy Monday team,\nWelcome to Week 9 - we're officially into the heaviest stretch of this block now, building toward our test week.\nVolume's low & intensity's high, so don't chase extra reps - chase clean, heavy ones.\nReach out if you need anything - jess@deucegym.com\n\n____________________________\n\n3-3-3-3\nBack Squat\n@ RPE 8.5\n4x 50' DB Suitcase Carry (ea)\n\nComplete 3 rounds for quality of:\n8 Eccentric Front Foot Elevated Split Squat (:03ea)\n12 DB 1-Leg Glute Bridge (ea)\n10 Goblet Lateral Lunge (ea)\n\nComplete 2 rounds for quality of:\n30 Heel Elevated Triple Drop Goblet Squat: 12-10-8 (drop weight each time)\n20 Paused Standing Calf Raise (:02)\n\n____________________________\n\n*OPTIONAL* Extra Finisher:\nEMOM 12:\nMin 1: 12/10 Cal Assault Bike\nMin 2: 10 Alt DB Snatch (50/30)\nMin 3: 14 Alt Lateral Plyo Skier Hop",
